## **Step 3: Setup Content Collection**

Edit **`src/content.config.ts`** di repo blog:

typescript

```typescript
const blogCollection = defineCollection({
  loader: glob({
    pattern: '**/*.{md,mdoc}',
    base: './src/content/blog',
  }),
  schema: z.object({
    title: z.string(),
    description: z.string().optional(),
    date: dateInSiteTimezone,
    tags: z.array(z.string()).optional(),
    categories: z
      .array(z.string())
      .or(z.array(z.array(z.string())))
      .optional(),
    // ... field lainnya
  }),
});
```

Pastikan **`mdoc`** ada di pattern glob agar file **`.mdoc`** dari Keystatic bisa diproses.

---

## **Step 4: Deploy Blog ke Cloudflare Pages**

{% table %}
- **Langkah**
- **Detail**
---
- Buka Cloudflare Dashboard
- **`https://dash.cloudflare.com`**
---
- Pages
- Create a project
---
- Connect to Git
- Pilih repo **`webku`**
---
- Build settings
- Framework: Astro, Build command: **`pnpm build`**, Output: **`dist`**
---
- Environment Variables
- Tambahkan **`NODE_VERSION=20`**
{% /table %}

Setelah deploy pertama, blog akan live di **`https://your-project.pages.dev`**.

Tambahkan custom domain di tab **Custom Domains** untuk menggunakan domain sendiri.

